ext_descriptions.ext_description:
An Item_proximity_relationship is a type of View_definition_relationship that defines an association between a and another that is near it.
Where applicable, the inherited relation_type attribute shall take one of the following values:
'space_to_element': the items_in_proximity bounds the space;
'penetration': the items_in_proximity penetrates or "goes through" the item;
'touch': the items_in_proximity is in contact with the item.
